He also has a competitive advantage over other entrepreneurs: he only demands the money when it arrives.
One of the new methods is the luxury ship scam: yachts are rented from Turkish ports supposedly to take American or European families on nice tourist cruises of a few days.
In reality, the ships are loaded with Syrians, Iraqis, Kurds and Afghans, who are transported for a fee of EUR 5 000 to EUR 7 000, first by land from Istanbul to a port and then by sea to Europe.
